		<paragraph indent="0" tabs="" style="normal" height="0" width="400" y="+6" x="12" type="text"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">This writing task asks about the 'benefits' and 'drawbacks' of a situation, which is the same as asking about its advantages and disadvantages. Before you do this exercise, spend a few minutes noting down what you think the advantages and disadvantages of free admission to museums are. Then, after you have done the exercise, compare your ideas with the ones mentioned by the people.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
